data.message: Research moodboard creation best practices: Compiled comprehensive findings from NN/g, Milanote, Figma, Eleken, and others. Documented 5-step process, moodboard structure (7 sections), distinction between moodboard vs competitive analysis board, and B2B SaaS specific considerations.
